<!doctype html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Conta criada</title>
  </head>
  <body style="margin:0;background:#F5F5F5;color:#262123;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;">
    <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" role="presentation" style="background:#F5F5F5;padding:24px 12px;">
      <tr>
        <td align="center">
          <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" role="presentation" style="max-width:680px;background:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid #E5E7EB;border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden;">
            <tr>
              <td style="background:#D90C2C;color:#FFFFFF;padding:24px;">
                <p style="margin:0 0 8px;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.04em;text-transform:uppercase;">Portal de Abatimentos Tirol</p>
                <h1 style="margin:0;font-size:24px;line-height:1.25;">Sua conta foi criada</h1>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td style="padding:24px;">
                <p style="margin:0 0 16px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6;">Ola, <strong><%= account.name %></strong>.</p>
                <p style="margin:0 0 18px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6;">A sua conta no Portal de Abatimentos Tirol foi criada. Use seu e-mail e a senha inicial abaixo para acessar.</p>

                <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" role="presentation" style="border:1px solid #E5E7EB;border-radius:10px;overflow:hidden;margin-bottom:20px;">
                  <tr>
                    <td style="padding:14px 16px;background:#FAFAFA;border-bottom:1px solid #E5E7EB;font-weight:700;">Dados de acesso</td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td style="padding:16px;">
                      <p style="margin:0 0 8px;"><strong>E-mail:</strong> <%= account.email %></p>
                      <p style="margin:0;"><strong>Senha inicial:</strong></p>
                      <p style="margin:10px 0 0;display:inline-block;background:#F5F5F5;border:1px solid #E5E7EB;border-radius:8px;padding:12px 14px;font-size:20px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.08em;"><%= password %></p>
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                </table>

                <p style="margin:0 0 18px;color:#6B7280;font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;">No primeiro acesso, o portal podera solicitar a alteracao dessa senha.</p>

                <a href="<%= portal_url %>" style="display:inline-block;background:#D90C2C;color:#FFFFFF;text-decoration:none;padding:12px 16px;border-radius:8px;font-weight:700;">Acessar portal</a>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </body>
</html>
